<LanguageData>

<VV_StatsReport_ManaStorage>Maximum Mana</VV_StatsReport_ManaStorage>
<VV_StatsReport_ManaStorage_Desc>The maximum amount of mana that can be held.</VV_StatsReport_ManaStorage_Desc>

<VV_StatsReport_ManaGenerate>Daily max mana production</VV_StatsReport_ManaGenerate>
<VV_StatsReport_ManaGenerate_Desc>The max amount of mana produced daily. Mana production varies depending on specific conditions.
\nMana that cannot be stored or exceeds the storage limit is converted into environmental mana, which slowly spreads through the surrounding land from the plant's current location and can be absorbed by other arcane plants.</VV_StatsReport_ManaGenerate_Desc>

<VV_StatsReport_ManaConsume>Daily max mana consumption</VV_StatsReport_ManaConsume>
<VV_StatsReport_ManaConsume_Desc>The max amount of mana consumed daily. Mana consumption varies depending on specific conditions.
\nIf the consumption exceeds production and there is no stored mana, the arcane plant will not function.</VV_StatsReport_ManaConsume_Desc>

<VV_StatsReport_ManaAbsorb>Daily mana absorption</VV_StatsReport_ManaAbsorb>
<VV_StatsReport_ManaAbsorb_Desc>The amount of environment mana that can be absorbed daily. If it lacks mana or is able to store more, it absorbs environmental mana for consumption.</VV_StatsReport_ManaAbsorb_Desc>

<VV_StatsReport_ManaPerShoot>Mana Consumption Per Shoot</VV_StatsReport_ManaPerShoot>
<VV_StatsReport_ManaPerShootDesc>The amount of mana consumed each time the weapon fires</VV_StatsReport_ManaPerShootDesc>

